# Where the deployed SPA reaches the API (ADR-0026).
#
# ⚠️ Baked into the bundle at BUILD time by Vite — it is PUBLIC, never a secret.
# Set the real value per environment in the Cloudflare Pages build settings
# (Production and Preview separately), not in a committed file.
#
# Dev does NOT need this: leave it unset and the Vite proxy forwards /api to
# the local Worker (wrangler dev, :8787).
#
# The Worker must allowlist the SPA's origin in its CORS_ORIGINS var
# (backend/wrangler.jsonc) — the two values change together.
VITE_API_URL=https://splitease-backend.YOUR-SUBDOMAIN.workers.dev
